<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧٢٦ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا عَلِيُّ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا بِشْرُ بْنُ الْمُفَضَّلِ: حَدَّثَنَا خَالِدُ بْنُ ذَكْوَانَ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ الرُّبَيِّعِ بِنْتِ مُعَوِّذٍ قَالَتْ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>كُنَّا مَعَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> نَسْقِي وَنُدَاوِي الْجَرْحَى، وَنَرُدُّ الْقَتْلَى<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِلَى الْمَدِينَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٢٧٢٧، ٥٣٥٥]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>